#

Tom Kha Gai (Thai Coconut Soup)

30 min
$15
400 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

ChickenCoconut

Dietary Tags:

Dairy-FreeGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Thai

Course:

Main

Tags:

SoupThaiComfort Food

Description

A rich and creamy coconut soup with tender chicken, fragrant herbs, and a hint of spice for a delightful warming dish.

Ingredients

  • chicken breast, sliced: 1 cup
  • coconut milk: 2 cups
  • chicken broth: 1 cup
  • mushrooms, sliced: 1 cup
  • lemongrass, chopped: 2 stalks
  • galangal, sliced (or ginger): 1 inch
  • kaffir lime leaves: 3 leaves
  • fish sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • cilantro, chopped: 1/4 cup
  • chili pepper, sliced: 1
  • sugar: 1 teaspoon
